, the authors draw a picture of financial literacy. They furthermore present a number of recommendations that help developing the knowledge and the financial skills of young people in practice.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aFinance, PersonalzGermany. 0aFinance, PersonalzPoland. 0aFinancial literacyzGermany. 0aFinancial literacyzPoland. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / General.2bisacsh1 aGrzesiuk, Aleksandra, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGrzesiuk, Aleksandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKorczak, Dieter, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKorczak, Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWyszkowska-Kaniewska, Olga, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWyszkowska-Kaniewska, Olga, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aŚwiecka, Beata Ś, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aŚwiecka, Beata, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2019z9783110606065oZDB-23-DBV08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Law & Social Sciences 2019 ENGz97831106101300 cEPUBz97831106330610 cprintz978311063296540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311063695640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110636956423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110636956.jpg  a978-3-11-061013-0  EBOOK PACKA